# Changelog FITTSMON

## 2025-04-18
- **Fork-1.0.1: Renamed from FittsTool to FittsMon due to improved monitor management.
- Force using default monitor.
- Improved configuration handling.
- Fixed several bugs related to multi-monitor support.

## 2009-03-29
- **FittsTool 1.0**: Initial release containing all planned features.
- Implemented basic corner and edge action binding.
- Added initial configuration file format.
